#: manifest.ini:changelog
msgid ""
"Version 0.5.5:\n"
"- Improved automatic language profile matching across CLD2 and Google TTS language-code aliases, including Filipino/Tagalog, Javanese, legacy Hebrew codes, Norwegian variants, Arabic, and Simplified, Traditional, and Cantonese Chinese mappings.\n"
"- Rebuilt the bundled CLD2 Windows DLLs with MSVC instead of MinGW-w64 so the packaged add-on no longer triggers the previous false-positive antivirus detection in VirusTotal testing."
msgstr ""
"0.5.5 版本：\n"
"- 改进了 CLD2 与 Google TTS 之间语言代码别名的自动语言配置文件匹配，包括菲律宾语（他加禄语）、爪哇语、旧版希伯来语代码、挪威语变体、阿拉伯语以及简体中文、繁体中文和粤语的映射。\n"
"- 使用 MSVC 替代 MinGW-w64 重新构建了随附的 Windows CLD2 DLL，使打包后的插件包在 VirusTotal 检测中不再像此前那样出现误报病毒的情况。"